➜英国数学专业面试有多难？牛剑面试真题你答得出来吗？
http://www.sohu.com/a/435797190_125528	24420
<p>数学是其实是一门“万金油”专业，毕业以后可以转向金融、管理、工程、计算机等方向，在应聘的时候，有时甚至比单一专业背景的毕业生更有竞争力。英国数学专业的教学质量一直不错，但是申请数学专业有时需要面试。英国数学专业面试有多难？小编带来了牛剑的面试真题，试试你能答出几道吧！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201202/6aa4a86fea6a4889a4c0b81cadb21c1d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>一、申请英国大学数学专业的要求</strong></p>
<p>我们先来看看牛津&amp;剑桥数学专业成绩要求：</p>
<p>1、牛津大学数学专业</p>
<p>A-level：A*A*A，数学和进阶数学成绩A*</p>
<p>面试比例：38%</p>
<p>成功申请比例：12%</p>
<p>被录取人数：182</p>
<p>2、剑桥大学数学专业</p>
<p>A-Level:A * A * A + STEP</p>
<p>IB：40-42分，HL成绩776+ STEP</p>
<p>申录比例：6:1</p>
<p>入学总人数：253</p>
<p><strong>二、牛剑数学面试真题</strong></p>
<p>牛剑大部分学院都会要求学生参加入学考试。由于新冠疫情的影响，今年牛剑部分面试会在线进行。牛剑面试题通常没有确切答案，重在评估面试者的面试过程。牛剑数学专业的面试题灵活性很高，找来了一些牛剑面试题，大家提前感受一下，看看自己的实力：</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>● Imagine a ladder leaning against a vertical wall with its feet on the ground. The middle rung of the ladder has been painted a different colour on the side, so that we can see it when we look at the ladder from the side on. What shape does that middle rung trace out as the ladder falls to the floor?（牛津数学专业面试真题）</p>
<p>● How many ways are there to cover a 2 x n rectangular grid with 2 x 1 tiles?（牛津数学专业面试真题）</p>
<p>●There's a torus/ring doughnut shaped space station with 2 spacemen on a spacewalk standing diametrically oppositie each other. Can then ask a variety of questions such as if spaceman A wants to throw a spanner to spaceman B, what angle and speed should they choose (stating any assumptions made, e.g. that gravity = 0)?（这道题目由牛津面试者提供）</p>
<p>● if your friends were here now instead of you, what would they say about you?（这是一道剑桥大学数学专业面试题，考察内容与数学无关，但考察面试者的综合能力）</p>
<p>● Integrate xlog(x).（牛津大学数学专业面试题）</p>
<p>● Differentiate x^x, then sketch it.（牛津大学数学专业面试题）</p>
<p>● If a cannon is pointed straight at a monkey in a tree, and the monkey lets go and falls towards the ground at the same instant the cannon is fired, will the monkey be hit? Describe any assumptions you make. （这是牛剑面试者分享的一道真题）</p>
<p>● If you could have half an hour with any mathematician past or present, who would it be?（牛剑面试者分享的一道真题，考察数学知识相关）</p>
<p>● Do you know where the multiplication sign came from？（牛津大学mathematics and statistics专业面试题）</p>
